| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3357 — Recovery Inhibition (darkrace)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c54ae114-b968-5592-8411-a8a2f0b5cb2e"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
